(C) Water levels: Low to normal due to dry fall. Heavy rains brought on high water in Dec. with rush of spawners.
(D) Spawning distribution: Spawning channels and from mouth to hatchery.
(E) Comments on predators: Lots of birds, some bears, people
(F) Egg digging: Some seen within reach below hatchery by Chum. No setimate on how many
(K) Additional comments: The runs in this river are counted by Big Qualicum hatchery staff on a regular basis.
